entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued October 08 at 2:14PM AKDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...Elevated Surf Possible Tuesday Through Thursday... West winds of 25 to 35 mph blowing over a 600 NM fetch of open water over the Arctic Ocean and Chukchi Sea will cause elevated water levels and elevated surf along the Arctic Coast from Tue through Thu. This will likely lead to beach erosion next week along the Arctic Coast.
